  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Furry Killer 2020 is the game that lets you kill furries endlessly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot furries in a endless 2D top down action packed adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun for the whole family!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417420/extras/73a8cf79a867dd54aa8d3aa1b4a1d97f.avif?t=1763925694\" width=450 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DISCLAIMER:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENDLESS FURRY KILLER 2020 DOES NOT </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONDONE OR SUPPORT ANY TYPE OF</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >REAL WORLD VIOLENCE OR HATE TOWARD</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ANY GROUP OF ANY KIND!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliminate Furries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2d Top Down Game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable Upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ammo, Health, Money Pickups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Difficulty Modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Map Variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Weapons, Pistol, Machine Gun, and Rail Gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grenades</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417420/extras/8d55933d486b4c38b7f7562601a20e65.avif?t=1763925694\" width=450 height=175 /></span></p>",
